# 🕷️ Agentic AI Web Scraping & Site Cloner

A Node.js CLI tool to **crawl, clone, and locally serve websites**.  
It fetches pages, assets (CSS, JS, images), rewrites links, and optionally spins up a local server to browse the cloned site.  
This project also leverages **OpenAI** (optional future enhancement) for intelligent content processing and cleaning.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🌐 Crawl and clone websites (pages + assets)
- 📂 Save cloned site to a local directory
- 🔗 Rewrites links for offline usage
- ⚡ Configurable concurrency and timeouts
- 🤖 Respects `robots.txt` (best effort)
- 🖥️ Serve locally with **Express**
- 🌍 Auto-open in default browser
- ✨ Built with:
  - `Node.js` (ESM modules)
  - `express`
  - `yargs` (CLI)
  - `got` (HTTP client)
  - `cheerio` (HTML parsing)
  - `p-limit` (concurrency control)
  - `ora` (CLI spinner)
  - `postcss` + `postcss-url` (optional CSS asset handling)
  - `openai` (optional, for AI-based analysis)

---

## 📦 Installation

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/satyasandhya97/agenticAIWebScraping.git
   cd agenticAIWebScraping

2. npm install

3. Add your API key in .env:-
   OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
 

4. Run the cli command in terminal:-
 node src/siteclone.js https://hitesh.ai/ --serve 3000 --open